variables.input:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallQueue"
| filter pstnConnectivityType == "DirectRouting"
| dedup call.id
| fields call.id

0.title: Call health
0.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallMetadata"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| fields callHealth

4.title: Total Call duration
4.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallMetadata"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| summarize avg(callDurationS)

12.title: Wait duration
12.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallQueue"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| summarize avg(callQueueDurationSeconds)

13.title: Call duration
13.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_AutoAttendant" 
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| join [ fetch logs
          | filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
          | filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallMetadata"
], on: { call.id }
| fields duration = right.callDurationS - duration

14.title: Agent name
14.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallQueue"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| filter isNotNull(agentName)
| fields agentName

15.title: Caller number
15.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_StreamDetails"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| filter matchesValue(caller.id, "+*")
| fields caller.id

16.title: Callee number
16.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_DirectRouting"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
//| filter matchesValue(caller.id, "+*")
| fields calleeNumber

17.title: Callee name
17.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_DirectRouting"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
//| filter matchesValue(caller.id, "+*")
| fields userDisplayName

18.title: IVR
18.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_AutoAttendant"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| fields autoAttendantCallFlow

19.title: Agent OptIn
19.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallQueue"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| filterOut isNull(callQueueAgentOptInCount)
| fields callQueueAgentOptInCount

20.title: Total Agent in Call Queue
20.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallQueue"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| filterOut isNull(callQueueAgentCount)
| fields callQueueAgentCount

21.title: Call terminated cause
21.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_DirectRouting"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| fields finalSipCodePhrase

22.title: SBC
22.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_DirectRouting"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| fields trunkFullyQualifiedDomainName

23.title: TransferAction
23.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_AutoAttendant"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| fields autoAttendantTransferAction

24.title: Connectivity Type
24.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_AutoAttendant"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| fields pstnConnectivityType

25.title: Call Success
25.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_DirectRouting"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| fields successfulCall

26.title: Waterfall Details
26.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_StreamDetails"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| dedup call.id
| fieldsAdd timeframe = timeframe(from:timestamp - 5m, to: timestamp + 5m)
| fields `Drilldown to App` = concat("[", call.id, "](https://eyx12671.apps.dynatrace.com/ui/apps/my.teams.observability/callOverview?callId=", call.id, "&start=", timeframe[start], "&end=", timeframe[end], ")")

27.title: Call startDateTime
27.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallMetadata"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| fields startDateTime

31.title: Auto Attendant Duration
31.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_AutoAttendant"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| summarize avg(autoAttendantChainDurationInSecs)

36.title: Call Queue Call Result
36.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallQueue"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| filterOut isNull(callQueueCallResult)
| fields callQueueCallResult

37.title: Call Queue Target
37.query:
fetch logs
| filter dt.system.bucket == "ms_teams"
| filter log.source == "MSTeams_CallRecords_CallQueue"
| filter in(call.id, array($callId))
| filterOut isNull(callQueueTargetType)
| fields callQueueTargetType
